Did you know you can throw away a black card by clicking/tapping on the X/trash can icon? Try doing it with this card, right now! Any black card that you throw away will be replaced with a new, fresh card from the deck. Black cards that are currently in someone else's hand will not be given to you as a replacement. So go ahead and give it a try!

You come in as a player in the card game! As a player, you have the ability to interact with the cards, including throwing away black cards that you don't want. When you throw away a black card, it will be replaced with a new one from the deck. This allows you to constantly refresh your options and strategize with different cards. So go ahead and give it a try by clicking/tapping on the X/trash can icon on a black card!
